name: The Accidental Influencer
overview: When Red’s boyfriend breaks up with her on her 30th birthday and throws himself at her new boss, she quits her job and signs up for a new Instagram account to start ranting about her shameless ex. Her life takes a dramatic turn when her posts go viral.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Red is unceremoniously dumped by her longtime boyfriend she had hoped to marry and quits her stable job. Pouring out her life grievances on social media, Red accidentally goes viral on Instagram.

episodes.name: When You Thought It Was Time
episodes.overview: After achieving her goal of owning an apartment, Red’s dream of marrying her boyfriend Chihming is shattered when she turns 30.

episodes.name: Red's Memory-Go-Round
episodes.overview: While trying to connect with Chihming after their breakup, Red discovers on Instagram that he left her for a mysterious woman.

episodes.name: It Fits the B*tch, But Not Me
episodes.overview: Red decides to post her first Instagram story to vent her frustrations.

episodes.name: You've Got To Earn Your Worth!
episodes.overview: Red tries to distract herself with work and finds a silverlining in her heartbreak.

episodes.name: A Heartbroken Red Is Smoking Hot
episodes.overview: Red regains some confidence but quits her job when she realizes who her ex's new girlfriend is.

episodes.name: There's No Place Like Home
episodes.overview: A family lunch exposes that Red is now loveless and jobless but Red realizes that her posts on Instagram have accidentally gone viral.

episodes.name: Vivian's Boyfriend Wants "More"
episodes.overview: Red gains massive popularity online, while Red and Clara help Vivian with an impromptu home cleaning session as her boyfriend decides to visit her sooner.

episodes.name: Legs Open, Hearts Open
episodes.overview: Red's confidence is shaken but makes a lifechanging decision to continue her social media account.

episodes.name: Blind Date Or Job Interview?
episodes.overview: Red fills her time with blind dates and job interviews and mistakes an interview for a date.

episodes.name: The Omnipresent Chihming Chou
episodes.overview: Red starts her new job while juggling being an influencer. News of JC's new fling surfaces on a gossip website.

episodes.name: Good Riddance Or Good To See You Again?
episodes.overview: Chihming's mother tries to talk Red into getting back with Chihming but she gets away by lying about a new boyfriend.

episodes.name: An Influencer's World Is A Rocky One
episodes.overview: Red realizes the rules of love. While Chihming hopes to reconcile Red.

episodes.name: What About My Happy Ending?
episodes.overview: An encounter between Red and Chihming forces Red to come to terms with the end of their relationship.
